ncis]] featuring Lovelytheband)}}\n| 2019\n| Brandon Dermer\n| <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q5AoVkBdhtA|title=Dillon Francis ft. lovelytheband \u2013 Change Your Mind (Official Music Video)|accessdate=October 9, 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n== Members ==\n*Sam Price - drums, percussion (2016-present)\n*Jordan Greenwald - guitar, keyboards (2016-present)\n*Mitch Collins - lead vocals, guitar (2016-present)\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n\n'''[[Billboard Music Awards]]'''\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Result\n! Reference\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\"|2019\n| [[Billboard Music Award for Top Rock Artist|Top Rock Artist]]\n| {{nominated}}\n|\n|-\n|Top Rock Song (\"Broken\")\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|}\n\n'''[[iHeartRadio Music Awards]]'''\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Result\n! Reference\n|-\n! rowspan=\"3\" | 2019\n| Best New Rock/Alternative Artist\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"3\" | <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/awards/8502606/heartradio-music-awards-2019-winners-list|title=Here Are All the Winners From the iHeartRadio Music Awards 2019|work=Billboard|accessdate=March 15, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| Alternative Rock Artist of the Year\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Alternative Rock Song of the Year (\"Broken\")\n| {{nom}}\n|}\n\n==Tour==\n===Headlining act===\n* Broken Like Me Tour (August\u2013October 2018) <ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.beyondthestagemagazine.com/lovelytheband-announce-headlining-tour/|title=Lovelytheband Announce Headlining tour|last=Flores|first=Bailey|accessdate=August 8, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180807220406/http://www.beyondthestagemagazine.com/lovelytheband-announce-headlining-tour/|archive-date=August 7, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* Finding It Hard to Smile Tour (2019)\n\n===Supporting act===\n* The Wrecks -  Robot Army Tour (November-December 2017) <ref>https://thesymphonyofrock.com/2017/10/05/the-wrecks-to-embark-on-robot-army-headlining-tour/</ref> <ref>https://www.instagram.com/p